FF9900\">主动：</span>德莱厄斯横扫面前的所有敌人，并将他们拉到自己身边。","leveltip":{"label":["无视护甲","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }}% -> {{ e1NL }}%","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[24,21,18,15,12],"cooldownBurn":"24/21/18/15/12","cost":[45,45,45,45,45],"costBurn":"45","effect":[null,[5,10,15,20,25],[10,12.5,15,17.5,20],[2,2,2,2,2]],"effectBurn":[null,"5/10/15/20/25","10/12.5/15/17.5/20","2"],"vars":[],"costType":"mana","range":[540,540,540,540,540],"rangeBurn":"540","image":{"full":"DariusAxeGrabCone.png","sprite":"spell1.png","group":"spell","x":240,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }}法力"},{"id":"DariusExecute","name":"诺克萨斯断头台","description":"德莱厄斯跃向目标英雄并进行致命打击，造成真实伤害。目标身上的每层出血效果都会提升这个技能的伤害。如果诺克萨斯断头台完成了一次击杀，那么它的冷却时间会暂时被重置。","tooltip":"跃向目标英雄并进行致命打击，造成{{ e1 }}<span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ f1 }})</span>真实伤害。 <br><br>目标身上的每层出血效果，都会使诺克萨斯断头台额外造成{{ e3 }}%的伤害。<br><span class=\"colorF50F00\">最大伤害值：{{ f3 }}</span><br><br>如果诺克萨斯断头台击杀了目标，那么德莱厄斯可以在接下来的20秒内再次施放诺克萨斯断头台。","leveltip":{"label":["冷却时间","基础伤害"],"effect":["{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}","{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[120,100,80],"cooldownBurn":"120/100/80","cost":[100,100,100],"costBurn":"100","effect":[null,[160,250,340],[50,50,50],[20,20,20]],"effectBurn":[null,"160/250/340","50","20"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":0.75,"key":"f1"},{"link":"@special.dariusr3","coeff":[160,250,340],"key":"f3"}],"costType":"mana","range":[460,460,460],"rangeBurn":"460","image":{"full":"DariusExecute.png","sprite":"spell1.png","group":"spell","x":288,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }}法力"}],"passive":{"name":"出血","description":"德莱厄斯将他的攻击瞄向目标的战略部位，让目标流血不止。这个效果最多可叠加5次。","image":{"full":"Darius_Icon_Hemorrhage.png","sprite":"passive0.png","group":"passive","x":192,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[{"champion":"Darius","title":"Beginner","type":"riot-beginner","map":"1","mode":"CLASSIC","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"beginner_Starter","items":[{"id":"1055","count":1},{